---
---

<section class="py-32 px-8 bg-surface-container">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1280px] flex flex-col gap-16">
    <h2 class="text-[36px] font-semibold leading-[1.3] tracking-[-0.02em] text-on-surface max-w-2xl">
      Três coisas que mudam sua rotina para sempre.
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded p-8 flex flex-col gap-6 h-full">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-primary">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[32px]">auto_awesome</span>
          <h3 class="text-[24px] font-semibold leading-[1.4] tracking-[-0.01em] text-on-surface">Agenda Inteligente</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-base leading-[1.6] text-on-surface-variant">
          Roteirização automática baseada em localização, prioridade do médico e histórico de prescrições.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-outline-variant">
          <div class="w-full h-32 bg-surface rounded flex items-center justify-center border border-outline-variant/50">
            <span class="text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-outline">VISUALIZAÇÃO DE MAPA</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded p-8 flex flex-col gap-6 h-full">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-tertiary">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[32px]">mic</span>
          <h3 class="text-[24px] font-semibold leading-[1.4] tracking-[-0.01em] text-on-surface">Voice + IA</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-base leading-[1.6] text-on-surface-variant">
          Dite o resumo da visita no corredor. Nossa IA estrutura os dados e atualiza o CRM automaticamente.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-outline-variant">
          <div class="w-full h-16 flex items-center justify-center gap-1 opacity-60">
            <div class="w-1 h-4 bg-tertiary rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-tertiary rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="w-1 h-12 bg-tertiary rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="w-1 h-6 bg-tertiary rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="w-1 h-10 bg-tertiary rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="w-1 h-3 bg-tertiary rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded p-8 flex flex-col gap-6 h-full">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-secondary">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[32px]">view_kanban</span>
          <h3 class="text-[24px] font-semibold leading-[1.4] tracking-[-0.01em] text-on-surface">Pipeline Visual</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-base leading-[1.6] text-on-surface-variant">
          Acompanhe o estágio de cada profissional com a clareza de um board Kanban cirúrgico.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-outline-variant flex flex-col gap-2">
          <div class="w-full h-8 bg-surface border border-outline-variant rounded px-2 flex items-center">
            <div class="w-1/3 h-1 bg-secondary rounded"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full h-8 bg-surface border border-outline-variant rounded px-2 flex items-center">
            <div class="w-2/3 h-1 bg-tertiary rounded"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
